{"header":"<h1>Module type <code><span>Svalue.Value_ext</span></code></h1>","type":"documentation","uses_katex":false,"breadcrumbs":[{"name":"Index","href":"../../../../../index.html","kind":"leaf-page"},{"name":"soteria","href":"../../../../index.html","kind":"page"},{"name":"Soteria","href":"../../../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"Bv_values","href":"../../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"Svalue","href":"../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"Value_ext","href":"#","kind":"module-type"}],"toc":[],"source_anchor":null,"preamble":"<p>How to embed a domain-specific <em>extension</em> into the otherwise fixed svalue grammar. An extension contributes:</p><ul><li>a new value leaf <code>t</code>, reachable through the <code>Extension</code> node, and</li><li>a new type <code>ty</code>, reachable through the <code>TExtension</code> type.</li></ul><p><a href=\"../Make/index.html\"><code>Make</code></a> weaves these into the value/type definitions and threads the operations below through hash-consing, evaluation, substitution and SMT encoding, so the extension behaves like a first-class part of the grammar. Tools needing no extra leaves use <a href=\"../Dummy_ext/index.html\"><code>Dummy_ext</code></a> instead.</p><p>Throughout, <code>super_t</code> is the <em>enclosing</em> svalue (the whole grammar, including this extension) and <code>super_ty</code> its type. Both stay polymorphic in the <code>'ghost</code> minted by <a href=\"../Make/index.html\"><code>Make</code></a>: an extension is defined before any application of <a href=\"../Make/index.html\"><code>Make</code></a>, so it cannot — and must not — name a concrete ghost. Each operation instead receives svalue-level callbacks already specialised to the embedding application's ghost, and applies them to the svalues nested inside an extension value.</p>","content":"<div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec type subst anchored\" id=\"type-{super_t}4/shadowed/(9c694a9d07b83afb3021ba21b34052f3)\"><a href=\"#type-{super_t}4/shadowed/(9c694a9d07b83afb3021ba21b34052f3)\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">type</span> <span>('ghost, 't, 'ty) {super_t}4/shadowed/(9c694a9d07b83afb3021ba21b34052f3)</span></span><span> :=\u000A  <span><span>(<span class=\"type-var\">'ghost</span>, <span class=\"type-var\">'t</span>, <span class=\"type-var\">'ty</span>)</span> <a href=\"../index.html#type-t\">t</a></span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p><code>_ super_t</code> is the enclosing svalue</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec type subst anchored\" id=\"type-{super_ty}5/shadowed/(9c694a9d07b83afb3021ba21b34052f3)\"><a href=\"#type-{super_ty}5/shadowed/(9c694a9d07b83afb3021ba21b34052f3)\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">type</span> <span>'ty {super_ty}5/shadowed/(9c694a9d07b83afb3021ba21b34052f3)</span></span><span> := <span><span class=\"type-var\">'ty</span> <a href=\"../index.html#type-ty\">ty</a></span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p><code>_ super_ty</code> is the enclosing svalue type</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec type anchored\" id=\"type-t\"><a href=\"#type-t\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">type</span> <span>'ghost t</span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Extension value leaves; appear in svalues through <code>Extension</code>.</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-equal\"><a href=\"#val-equal\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> equal : \u000A  <span><span>(<span><span class=\"type-var\">'ghost</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><span class=\"type-var\">'ghost</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span class=\"xref-unresolved\">Ppx_deriving_runtime</span>.bool)</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A  <span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'ghost</span> <a href=\"#type-t\">t</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A  <span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'ghost</span> <a href=\"#type-t\">t</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A  <span class=\"xref-unresolved\">Ppx_deriving_runtime</span>.bool</span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-compare\"><a href=\"#val-compare\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> compare : \u000A  <span><span>(<span><span class=\"type-var\">'ghost</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><span class=\"type-var\">'ghost</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span class=\"xref-unresolved\">Ppx_deriving_runtime</span>.int)</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A  <span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'ghost</span> <a href=\"#type-t\">t</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A  <span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'ghost</span> <a href=\"#type-t\">t</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A  <span class=\"xref-unresolved\">Ppx_deriving_runtime</span>.int</span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec type anchored\" id=\"type-ty\"><a href=\"#type-ty\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">type</span> <span>'ghost ty</span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Extension types; appear in svalue types through <code>TExtension</code>.</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-equal_ty\"><a href=\"#val-equal_ty\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> equal_ty : \u000A  <span><span>(<span><span class=\"type-var\">'ghost</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><span class=\"type-var\">'ghost</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span class=\"xref-unresolved\">Ppx_deriving_runtime</span>.bool)</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A  <span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'ghost</span> <a href=\"#type-ty\">ty</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A  <span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'ghost</span> <a href=\"#type-ty\">ty</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A  <span class=\"xref-unresolved\">Ppx_deriving_runtime</span>.bool</span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-compare_ty\"><a href=\"#val-compare_ty\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> compare_ty : \u000A  <span><span>(<span><span class=\"type-var\">'ghost</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><span class=\"type-var\">'ghost</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span class=\"xref-unresolved\">Ppx_deriving_runtime</span>.int)</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A  <span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'ghost</span> <a href=\"#type-ty\">ty</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A  <span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'ghost</span> <a href=\"#type-ty\">ty</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A  <span class=\"xref-unresolved\">Ppx_deriving_runtime</span>.int</span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec type subst anchored\" id=\"type-super_ty\"><a href=\"#type-super_ty\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">type</span> <span>'g super_ty</span></span><span> := <span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-ty\">ty</a></span> <a href=\"../index.html#type-ty\">ty</a></span></span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec type subst anchored\" id=\"type-super_t\"><a href=\"#type-super_t\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">type</span> <span>'g super_t</span></span><span> := <span><span>(<span class=\"type-var\">'g</span>, <span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-t\">t</a></span>, <span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-ty\">ty</a></span>)</span> <a href=\"../index.html#type-t\">t</a></span></span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-pp\"><a href=\"#val-pp\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> pp : <span><span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-super_t\">super_t</a></span> <span class=\"xref-unresolved\">Fmt</span>.t</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-t\">t</a></span> <span class=\"xref-unresolved\">Fmt</span>.t</span></span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-pp_ty\"><a href=\"#val-pp_ty\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> pp_ty : <span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-ty\">ty</a></span> <span class=\"xref-unresolved\">Fmt</span>.t</span></span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-iter_vars\"><a href=\"#val-iter_vars\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> iter_vars : <span><span>(<span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-super_t\">super_t</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> unit)</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-t\">t</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> unit</span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-hash\"><a href=\"#val-hash\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> hash : <span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-t\">t</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> int</span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-hash_ty\"><a href=\"#val-hash_ty\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> hash_ty : <span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-ty\">ty</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> int</span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-mk\"><a href=\"#val-mk\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> mk : <span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-super_ty\">super_ty</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-t\">t</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><span>(<span class=\"type-var\">'g</span>, <span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-t\">t</a></span>, <span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-ty\">ty</a></span>)</span> <a href=\"../index.html#type-t_kind\">t_kind</a></span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p><code>mk ty x</code> is the svalue node-kind representing extension value <code>x</code> at type <code>ty</code> — typically <code>Extension x</code>, but the extension may normalise to another kind. <a href=\"../Make/index.html\" title=\"Soteria.Bv_values.Svalue.Make\"><code>Make</code></a> hash-conses the result. Called when an svalue carrying an extension is rebuilt (e.g. after its children are evaluated).</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-eval\"><a href=\"#val-eval\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> eval : <span><span>(<span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-super_t\">super_t</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-super_t\">super_t</a></span>)</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-t\">t</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-t\">t</a></span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p><code>eval eval_super x</code> returns <code>x</code> with every enclosing svalue nested in it replaced by <code>eval_super</code> applied to it — the extension's contribution to the <a href=\"../../Eval/index.html\" title=\"Soteria.Bv_values.Eval\"><code>Eval</code></a> pass.</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-apply_subst\"><a href=\"#val-apply_subst\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> apply_subst : \u000A  <span><span>(<span><span class=\"label\">missing_var</span>:<span>(<span><a href=\"../../../Symex/Var/index.html#type-t\">Var.t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-super_ty\">super_ty</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-super_t\">super_t</a></span>)</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A    <span><span class=\"type-var\">'subst</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A    <span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-super_t\">super_t</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A    <span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-super_t\">super_t</a></span> * <span class=\"type-var\">'subst</span>)</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A  <span><span class=\"label\">missing_var</span>:<span>(<span><a href=\"../../../Symex/Var/index.html#type-t\">Var.t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-super_ty\">super_ty</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-super_t\">super_t</a></span>)</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A  <span><span class=\"type-var\">'subst</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A  <span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-t\">t</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A  <span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-t\">t</a></span> * <span class=\"type-var\">'subst</span></span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-encode_ty\"><a href=\"#val-encode_ty\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> encode_ty : <span><span>(<span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-super_ty\">super_ty</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <a href=\"../../../Smt/index.html#type-sexp\">Smt.sexp</a>)</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-ty\">ty</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <a href=\"../../../Smt/index.html#type-sexp\">Smt.sexp</a></span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-encode_value\"><a href=\"#val-encode_value\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> encode_value : <span><span>(<span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-super_t\">super_t</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <a href=\"../../../Smt/index.html#type-sexp\">Smt.sexp</a>)</span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'g</span> <a href=\"#type-t\">t</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <a href=\"../../../Smt/index.html#type-sexp\">Smt.sexp</a></span></code></div></div>"}